    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep luster without a single chip or scratch, while the interior remains pristine and free of any wear. Every mechanical and electronic system functions perfectly, offering a driving experience that is tight, quiet, and powerful. For the discerning buyer seeking a collector-grade example, this car is truly as good as it gets.",
      "price": 49000.0,
